{"tid":1044514,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"普捷天奴：我們是較佳的一隊，若然那樣輸掉就是羞辱。","createTime":"2019-03-03T03:21:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T06:20:37.000Z","uid":3017,"like":33,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ecc82a81462441706e35d985c101d6e10c13b7e0","tid":1044514,"uid":3017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:21:09.000Z","msg":"普捷天奴：洛里斯撲救係大壽禮<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyEAESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=878c2f86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】熱刺未能以一場勝利，慶祝領隊普捷天奴47歲生日，不過壽星公認為洛里斯完場前的撲救，對他而言已是一大壽禮。<br />\n<br />\n普捷天奴賽後說：「是的，洛里斯的救球是一大禮物。我很開心，因為我們不值得輸掉這場比賽，因為我們是較佳的一隊，若然那樣輸掉就是羞辱。」完場階段，奧巴美揚禁區內博得達雲臣山齊士犯規，但他親自主射被洛里斯擋出，錯過為阿仙奴絕殺的機會。<br />\n<br />\n「我為球隊的演出感到開心，與阿仙奴對陣是一場硬仗，但我為球隊經過兩連敗後取得正面戰果感到開心，有助下周二對多蒙特，爭取晉身下一階段建立信心。」熱刺首回合領先3:0，晉級形勢大好。<br />\n<br />\n談到哈利卡尼獲12碼前有越位之嫌：「如果你問我關於越位，你得問問格列沙加在12分鐘如何對待卡尼，那沒有被吹罰。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n究竟點解有人會撐熱狗呢隊波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a3d07b7fa8104b7bf1c3b16764438328f93ed10","tid":1044514,"uid":41613,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:22:50.000Z","msg":"熱狗真係狗隊來"},{"pid":"0786ecd9fbee8b550fc66dba215de257347d9f56","tid":1044514,"uid":11254,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:23:56.000Z","msg":"兩大賤種 熱+皇"},{"pid":"3b7e1a6184bd77f45eba4d7033b0cc0482e7514a","tid":1044514,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:24:15.000Z","msg":"計點數係贏"},{"pid":"663f7e6897855ef4b02b5799030dc8c98d00cd47","tid":1044514,"uid":1823,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:25:08.000Z","msg":"格鬥黎講的確係較佳"},{"pid":"6d79b9312c5cd1fe0e5247631d7131d9f1154189","tid":1044514,"uid":41524,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:26:35.000Z","msg":"班賤種抵長期冇盃"},{"pid":"6f71989bb9c4e3f4fd079db0c96f72fef6fe2a18","tid":1044514,"uid":30804,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:27:01.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啦普捷天奴<br />\n穿心腿又點計<br />\n山齊士明抽水踏高斯尼點計<br />\n食屎狗<br />\n自己隊波靠offside先黑嗰十二碼仲咁多野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正一食屎狗<br />\n所以話熱由上到下都係仆街<br />\n冇咩球隊可以黑人憎得過熱"},{"pid":"9ecdc06237655bae783a06d6c76483400eb7795c","tid":1044514,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:28:37.000Z","msg":"自信從何來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a2d7bdfb554b345d58c1d3a0dd3f9dda35fa658","tid":1044514,"uid":192953,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:28:57.000Z","msg":"犯規，黑哨嗰方面較佳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce10bc4b090a47ba78d50320b666e272e2dbb57","tid":1044514,"uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:31:47.000Z","msg":"熱狗上上下下都係賤種"},{"pid":"15ae708a2023e57918fe0db2eeb0dcab591d1c30","tid":1044514,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:36:06.000Z","msg":"賤種熱狗"},{"pid":"407c2d2b612eacfa5dd08804e782c6c8532a3d25","tid":1044514,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a2d7bdfb554b345d58c1d3a0dd3f9dda35fa658","tid":1044514,"uid":192953,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:28:57.000Z","msg":"犯規，黑哨嗰方面較佳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:36:36.000Z","msg":"咁又係, 唔會有牌"},{"pid":"d83180bedc0e3d690fcadef4cd3fd075661633a3","tid":1044514,"uid":53803,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:48:44.000Z","msg":"熱狗冇公關？<br />\n成日俾條阿根廷佬係到鳩up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到熱神憎鬼厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eaeb9644ef572f17bfe3f53862092a452b5f535","tid":1044514,"uid":13275,"l